  +baselayout-1.12.0_pre6-r3.ebuild:
  Fix rc-daemon.sh signal handling, bug #103182

*baselayout-1.12.0_pre6-r2 (23 Aug 2005)
*baselayout-1.11.13-r1 (23 Aug 2005)

  23 Aug 2005; Mike Frysinger <vapier@gentoo.org>
